nodes.text: Jens Møller is an animator and director who has worked on several LEGO Star Wars projects including LEGO Star Wars: The Yoda Chronicles and LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures. He directed the Freemaker Adventures episodes "Peril on Kashyyyk", "The Kyber Saber Crystal Chase", and "Duel of Destiny". Møller also worked as assistant director for "The Maker of Zoh". In addition, Møller has worked on other projects including Lego Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu, Friends Forever, and Help! I'm a Fish.
